4
00:01:47,919 --> 00:01:49,852
Lin Qi Le.

5
00:01:53,219 --> 00:01:55,368
Are you feeling better?

6
00:01:57,819 --> 00:02:01,000
Yes, thanks for asking.

7
00:02:01,579 --> 00:02:04,059
Jiang Qiao Xi bought this for you.

8
00:02:06,540 --> 00:02:08,780
What do you mean by that?

9
00:02:09,740 --> 00:02:12,879
I know what happened between you two.

10
00:02:12,879 --> 00:02:15,439
You were very good friends

11
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:19,799
and close playmates as children.

12
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:34,108
You found out?

13
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:37,539
Did Jiang Qiao Xi tell you?

14
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:45,279
You and Jiang Qiao Xi…

15
00:02:47,419 --> 00:02:51,380
He and I…

16
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:58,960
at this point, can only be classmates 
 who study and support each other.

17
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:05,799
Once we're in college, we'll see how it goes.

18
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:14,780
Your relationship is none of my business.

19
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:17,799
Still, Jiang Qiao Xi values you as a friend.

20
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:29,600
I share his concerns 
 and see his friends as mine,

21
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:33,980
so I was worried when you passed out.

22
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:51,456
Thanks,

23
00:03:52,059 --> 00:03:54,990
but I already have enough friends.

24
00:03:54,990 --> 00:03:56,930
I have no need for more.

25
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,000
Why don't we stop now?

26
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:35,060
You had a heatstroke today. 
 You might feel sick again.

27
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:41,899
Lin Cherry, are you in a bad mood?

28
00:04:41,899 --> 00:04:44,500
No, I'm in a great mood!

29
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:47,779
I just want to learn how to ride a bike quickly 
 and strengthen my body

30
00:04:47,779 --> 00:04:50,320
so I can ride with all of you to school.

31
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:53,139
I don't want to repeat today's events.

32
00:04:53,139 --> 00:04:55,419
Did Jiang Qiao Xi upset you?

33
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:59,020
How could he possibly upset me?

34
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:03,620
You're lying.

35
00:05:03,620 --> 00:05:09,100
 Yun Yun! Yun Yun! 
 Help me with the accounts. 

36
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:12,180
Watch out for yourself. 
 Don't die because of Jiang Qiao Xi.

37
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:14,340
Get going already.

38
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:31,880
 He and I at this point, can only be classmates 
 who study and support each other. 

39
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:37,339
 Once we're in college, we'll see how it goes. 

40
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,860
I made it!

41
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,640
Look ahead!

42
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,176
Don't be afraid!

43
00:06:39,176 --> 00:06:40,000
Let go!

44
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,819
Let me help you, or you'll fall off the bike!

45
00:06:41,819 --> 00:06:43,040
- Don't… 
 - It's okay.

46
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,780
- Leave me alone! 
 - Careful!

47
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,700
Are you all right?

48
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:01,839
Wait, your arm…

49
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,499
Jiang Qiao Xi, what exactly do you want?

50
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:10,259
I saw you bicycling from upstairs.

51
00:07:10,259 --> 00:07:12,240
No one was with you. 
 I was afraid you'd fall, so I—

52
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,244
That's not what I meant!

53
00:07:14,939 --> 00:07:18,279
Didn't we agree to act like strangers?

54
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:20,199
We're not friends anymore.

55
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:24,479
How can you just show up 
 as if nothing happened?

56
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:32,620
I… I want to start things over with you.

57
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:34,459
Let's be friends again.

58
00:07:34,459 --> 00:07:36,640
You, as Lin Qi Le.

59
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:41,536
If I'm Lin Qi Le, 
 then am I no longer Lin Cherry?

60
00:07:41,536 --> 00:07:42,680
No, that's not what I mean—

61
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,999
All right, I get it.

62
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,900
Well, let me tell you.

63
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:51,899
If I am Lin Qi Le, 
 then I don't want to know you.

64
00:07:51,899 --> 00:07:57,420
If I am Lin Cherry, 
 then I wish I had never met you.

65
00:08:02,779 --> 00:08:04,219
You're hurt. Let me take you—

66
00:08:04,219 --> 00:08:06,339
Stay back! Don't come near me!

67
00:08:06,339 --> 00:08:10,600
Every time you get close to me, I get hurt! 
 Genuinely hurt!

68
00:08:11,899 --> 00:08:13,399
You're doing quite well now.

69
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:14,560
I'm doing well, too.

70
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:17,359
There's no need to start things over.

71
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,339
Cherry, I… I really didn't mean to—

72
00:08:20,339 --> 00:08:25,439
Enough! Let's just be regular classmates.

73
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:29,860
I won't bother you, 
 and you shouldn't bother me.

74
00:08:30,599 --> 00:08:32,376
All right?

75
00:08:36,579 --> 00:08:38,320
I'm sorry.

76
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:43,390
I didn't know I'd cause you so much trouble.

77
00:08:44,379 --> 00:08:46,470
If you feel sorry,

78
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,370
then promise me you'll stay away from me.

79
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:05,140
Let go!

80
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:41,539
 February 9, 2001. 

81
00:09:41,539 --> 00:09:43,840
 We have a computer at home now. 

82
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:47,299
 Uncle Cai says the whole world 
 is using the Internet now. 

83
00:09:47,299 --> 00:09:49,399
 We can't fall behind. 

84
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:53,159
 I bet Jiang Qiao Xi 
 has a computer at home, too. 

85
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:55,980
 They say you can chat online. 

86
00:09:55,980 --> 00:09:58,439
 I want to chat with Jiang Qiao Xi. 

87
00:09:58,439 --> 00:10:01,799
 Why does he never call me? 

88
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:04,860
 October 26th, 2001. 

89
00:10:04,860 --> 00:10:07,556
 Dad gave me three Harry Potter books. 

90
00:10:07,556 --> 00:10:10,659
 Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban, 

91
00:10:10,659 --> 00:10:12,390
 I held back from reading it. 

92
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:14,930
I want to read it with Jiang Qiao Xi.

93
00:10:14,939 --> 00:10:18,220
 May 26th, 2003. 

94
00:10:18,220 --> 00:10:21,319
 News reports say SARS 
 has reached the provincial city. 

95
00:10:21,319 --> 00:10:25,140
 A classmate's parents 
 returned from the provincial city today, 

96
00:10:25,140 --> 00:10:28,260
 and he was taken home. 

97
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:31,220
 - August 27th, 2004. 
 - He is so amazing! He won! 

98
00:10:31,220 --> 00:10:36,179
 - Liu Xiang broke the Olympic record and made history. 
 - He is so amazing! 

99
00:10:36,179 --> 00:10:40,200
 Watching the competition on TV 
 made me so happy, 

100
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:44,479
 because at that moment, 
 I didn't think of Jiang Qiao Xi. 

101
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:48,819
 February 9th, 2005. 

102
00:10:48,819 --> 00:10:52,499
 I didn't think about Jiang Qiao Xi today. 

103
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:06,919
 Cherry, I've never forgotten those days 
 we spent at Qunshan. 

104
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:12,579
 One day, I will personally deliver 
 these letters to you. 

105
00:11:17,019 --> 00:11:20,120
 Mom! Mom, don't tear them! Don't— 

106
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,812
 Go away! 

107
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:45,460
 September 16th, 2006. 

108
00:11:46,079 --> 00:11:49,380
 I won't let him hurt me anymore. 

109
00:12:29,140 --> 00:12:31,659
- I told you so. 
 - Exactly.

110
00:12:31,659 --> 00:12:35,640
By the way, it seems Jiang Qiao Xi 
 has cooled toward Lin Qi Le.

111
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,520
I think so, too. 
 He finally came to his senses.

112
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,679
Exactly.

113
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:40,919
Lin Qi Le is no match for Cen Xiao Man.

114
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:44,140
I believe Jiang Qiao Xi and Cen Xiao Man 
 are the best fit.

115
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:46,440
Who does Lin Qi Le think she is?

116
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:56,220
What is so great about Jiang Qiao Xi?

117
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:59,519
Don't mention me 
 when you gossip about him.

118
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:31,259
You three should go eat if you're done. 
 Don't worry about me.

119
00:13:31,259 --> 00:13:34,539
I'm feeling generous today 
 and can't stand to see people suffer.

120
00:13:34,539 --> 00:13:36,940
Let me help you clean up!

121
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:39,680
Cherry, let me help you, too.

122
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:42,419
The two of you 
 should be enough to help her.

123
00:13:42,419 --> 00:13:45,359
I'm going to eat now.

124
00:13:46,379 --> 00:13:49,580
If you're truly generous, pack me some food

125
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:54,019
so I have something to eat later.

126
00:13:54,019 --> 00:13:57,259
Can you manage if we leave you here alone?

127
00:13:57,259 --> 00:14:01,299
What a weird question! 
 Why can't I manage on my own?

128
00:14:04,139 --> 00:14:06,379
Go on. I've got this.

129
00:14:06,379 --> 00:14:08,224
- Go eat. Go! 
 - It's all right.

130
00:14:08,224 --> 00:14:09,280
Fang Yuan, go!

131
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,816
Go on. Go!

132
00:14:10,816 --> 00:14:12,928
Go eat.

133
00:14:12,928 --> 00:14:16,039
I can do it on my own. Get going!

134
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:18,600
I got it.

135
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:21,059
We'll get you some food.

136
00:15:13,059 --> 00:15:14,996
Meow!

137
00:15:18,279 --> 00:15:20,192
Meow!

138
00:15:26,100 --> 00:15:30,720
Little kitty, why are you here?

139
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:34,759
Which angel built you this little nest?

140
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:41,020
You can rub its chin. Cats like that.

141
00:15:41,020 --> 00:15:42,544
Try it.

142
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:51,819
In a few days, 
 I'm leaving for Olympiad training

143
00:15:51,819 --> 00:15:53,779
and won't be around.

144
00:15:53,779 --> 00:15:56,679
Could you take care of it for me?

145
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,640
Is this cat yours?

146
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:08,579
I found it last semester 
 before you transferred here.

147
00:16:08,699 --> 00:16:13,559
It was tiny. 
 It looked more like a little rabbit, not a kitten.

148
00:16:13,559 --> 00:16:15,819
Just like Chun Lu.

149
00:16:15,819 --> 00:16:18,019
Don't mention Chun Lu.

150
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:22,510
Cherry,

151
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:26,320
I really miss it.

152
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:28,759
But you already have a cat.

153
00:16:28,759 --> 00:16:32,580
Jiang Qiao Xi, you may like this cat

154
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:38,000
because it plays with you, 
 meows and catches mice,

155
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:41,779
but not because it looks like Chun Lu.

156
00:16:41,779 --> 00:16:44,500
Is Chun Lu easily replaceable?

157
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:46,980
Besides, a cat is a cat, 
 and a rabbit is a rabbit.

158
00:16:46,980 --> 00:16:48,759
How are they similar?

159
00:16:48,759 --> 00:16:51,519
I didn't replace Chun Lu with the kitten.

160
00:16:52,400 --> 00:16:57,659
It just keeps me company. 
 It helps ease my mind when I'm upset.

161
00:16:57,659 --> 00:16:59,600
Missing Chun Lu is another matter.

162
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:02,600
You are not allowed to miss Chun Lu.

163
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,960
I forbid you!

164
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:06,720
Why can't I miss Chun Lu?

165
00:17:08,299 --> 00:17:11,439
I held back and didn't approach you.

166
00:17:11,439 --> 00:17:13,259
In fact, I've kept my distance.

167
00:17:13,259 --> 00:17:16,820
Why deny me the right to miss Chun Lu?

168
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:18,319
Lin Qi Le, you're too bossy!

169
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:20,340
You're too shameless!

170
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:23,160
Why am I shameless? Chun Lu was also mine.

171
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:25,540
I had many good memories with it 
 which belong to me!

172
00:17:25,540 --> 00:17:28,699
Do whatever you want, but don't push it!

173
00:17:28,699 --> 00:17:30,340
But you already have a cat!

174
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:31,840
What's wrong with having a cat?

175
00:17:31,840 --> 00:17:33,619
I truly like it,

176
00:17:33,619 --> 00:17:35,820
but I also love Chun Lu.

177
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:41,880
How can you say that?

178
00:17:42,560 --> 00:17:44,599
Don't!

179
00:17:44,599 --> 00:17:46,719
Put it down!

180
00:17:46,719 --> 00:17:48,736
What are you doing?

181
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:52,599
Step back, all of you!

182
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:57,050
Why did you gather here?

183
00:17:57,050 --> 00:17:58,930
Are you going to fight?

184
00:18:00,279 --> 00:18:03,399
Jiang Qiao Xi, what happened?

185
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:07,000
She threw rocks at me.

186
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:11,279
Principal, it happened on school grounds. 
 Isn't this considered bullying?

187
00:18:11,279 --> 00:18:13,099
Principal, we saw the whole thing.

188
00:18:13,099 --> 00:18:15,859
Jiang Qiao Xi 
 started the argument with Lin Qi Le,

189
00:18:15,859 --> 00:18:18,120
who threw rocks at him in return.

190
00:18:18,120 --> 00:18:21,420
We only had a brief argument. 
 Did she really have to throw rocks at me?

191
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:24,120
"An argument"? 
 What were you arguing about?

192
00:18:29,079 --> 00:18:31,860
She wouldn't let me do what I wanted.

193
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:34,420
- Jiang Qiao Xi— 
 - Let him talk.

194
00:18:35,759 --> 00:18:37,364
Go on.

195
00:18:37,364 --> 00:18:39,440
She was bothering me.

196
00:18:42,179 --> 00:18:44,400
How did you bother him?

197
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,579
What were you doing here?

198
00:18:48,519 --> 00:18:53,470
I… I was cleaning up,

199
00:18:53,470 --> 00:18:55,740
and he came over.

200
00:18:58,340 --> 00:19:02,140
Did she bother you 
 while she was cleaning up?

201
00:19:02,140 --> 00:19:04,579
Then why did she throw rocks at you?

202
00:19:06,759 --> 00:19:11,700
I said something that made her angry.

203
00:19:11,700 --> 00:19:14,480
What did you say? Did you curse at her?

204
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:16,680
Does that justify it?

205
00:19:24,559 --> 00:19:28,880
Be sure you strictly follow 
 the school's rules and regulations.

206
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:31,759
Regardless of his identity 
 or academic performance,

207
00:19:31,759 --> 00:19:33,900
he can't stop you from doing your job.

208
00:19:33,900 --> 00:19:37,239
If it ever happens again, 
 come directly to my office.

209
00:19:37,239 --> 00:19:40,199
Don't start a fight, all right?

210
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:47,220
And you! You're strong and tall.

211
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:48,460
Why didn't you help?

212
00:19:48,460 --> 00:19:50,180
All three of you, remember

213
00:19:50,180 --> 00:19:52,960
that in this kind of situation, 
 you should step in to help.

214
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:05,519
Jiang Qiao Xi, you may have good grades,

215
00:20:06,339 --> 00:20:08,659
but you shouldn't be self-centered.

216
00:20:08,659 --> 00:20:11,319
You have indeed won some awards 
 for our school,

217
00:20:11,319 --> 00:20:15,380
but grades are not our only concern 
 in this high school.

218
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:17,979
Didn't you say she bothered you 
 while she was cleaning up?

219
00:20:17,979 --> 00:20:20,820
Fine, she'll stop cleaning up.

220
00:20:20,820 --> 00:20:25,080
You'll finish the cleaning yourself.

221
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:27,360
Come to my office after you're done.

222
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:29,600
There's no need, Principal.

223
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:31,119
I can clean up on my own.

224
00:20:31,119 --> 00:20:34,340
I can handle my own tasks. 
 I don't need help.

225
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:38,040
I… I did make some noise on purpose,

226
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:41,559
which disturbed and angered him, 
 so it wasn't his fault.

227
00:20:41,559 --> 00:20:43,140
- Did you do it on purpose? 
 - Yes.

228
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:44,400
Principal, that's not how it happened.

229
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:47,564
It wasn't on purpose. It was just normal noise. 
 I'm the one who bothered her.

230
00:20:47,564 --> 00:20:50,120
It wasn't normal at all. I did it on purpose.

231
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:51,539
I just can't stand him.

232
00:20:51,539 --> 00:20:53,199
He has good grades and is hardworking.

233
00:20:53,199 --> 00:20:56,180
- That's not true, Principal. Lin— 
 - It is, Principal.

234
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:59,740
What's going on with you two?

235
00:21:05,599 --> 00:21:08,260
We are equally responsible.

236
00:21:08,260 --> 00:21:09,696
I apologize.

237
00:21:09,696 --> 00:21:11,959
I'm sorry, Jiang Qiao Xi.

238
00:21:12,519 --> 00:21:14,180
I'm sorry, Lin Qi Le.

239
00:21:14,180 --> 00:21:16,500
I shouldn't have made you upset.

240
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:22,520
Good! As expected of our students! 
 It's great to see you admit your mistakes.

241
00:21:23,599 --> 00:21:25,472
It promotes unity.

242
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:29,599
 Goodbye, Principal. 

243
00:22:17,599 --> 00:22:21,399
Don't you think Lin Cherry 
 has been confusing

244
00:22:21,399 --> 00:22:23,060
ever since she began acting like a girl?

245
00:22:23,060 --> 00:22:24,180
"Confusing"?

246
00:22:24,180 --> 00:22:27,859
It's a strategic move 
 to stay away from Jiang Qiao Xi.

247
00:22:27,859 --> 00:22:30,580
When did you become an expert on girls?

248
00:22:31,559 --> 00:22:34,499
You guys should read some romance novels

249
00:22:34,499 --> 00:22:38,559
and get to know the other 50% 
 of the world's population.

250
00:22:40,759 --> 00:22:42,424
Show me!

251
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:48,080
"Wolf's Temptation!"

252
00:22:48,080 --> 00:22:50,720
Is there a romance novel 
 with a title like that?

253
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:53,619
The title is a little strange, 
 but it's quite trendy.

254
00:22:53,619 --> 00:22:55,759
Many girls in our class read it.

255
