296
00:25:36,959 --> 00:25:38,940
Yu Jin ate six packs of crunchy noodles…

297
00:25:38,940 --> 00:25:39,979
I won't talk to her again.

298
00:25:39,979 --> 00:25:42,599
just to win a card for Qin Ye Yun.

299
00:25:42,599 --> 00:25:46,260
