Lin Cherry,

307
00:27:00,100 --> 00:27:03,460
What did you discuss 
 with Jiang Qiao Xi yesterday?

308
00:27:03,460 --> 00:27:05,099
The two of you were ready to fight.

309
00:27:05,099 --> 00:27:07,480
