 - I'll say it anyway!

328
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:29,699
You are the rabbit, 
 and Cen Xiao Man is the cat!

329
00:28:29,699 --> 00:28:31,500
- Don't! You! 
 - That's what you meant!

330
00:28:31,500 --> 00:28:32,919
Stop it, Qin Ye Yun!

331
00:28:32,919 --> 00:28:35,239
You're the rabbit, 
 and Cen Xiao Man is the cat!

332
00:28:35,239 --> 00:28:38,159
You're the rabbit! You're the cat!

333
00:28:38,159 --> 00:28:40,619
Just admit defeat!

334
00:28:42,299 --> 00:28:44,159
No more lying. All right?

335
00:28:44,159 --> 00:28:46,239
I won't talk to you.

336
00:28:57,700 --> 00:29:01,179
Don't mention Jiang Qiao Xi again.

337
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:06,919
You say you hate him, 
 yet you still hope he is doing well.

338
