346
00:29:43,339 --> 00:29:45,019
I just tricked him.

347
00:29:45,019 --> 00:29:48,640
I told him he had to exchange secrets 
 with people he liked,

348
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:50,759
so he told me his secret,

349
00:29:50,759 --> 00:29:52,439
and I threatened him a little.

