Actually, it is wrong.

355
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,752
He shouldn't like me.

356
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,259
 Whose coat is this? 

357
00:30:28,259 --> 00:30:30,280
 Cherry, is this yours? 

358
00:30:30,280 --> 00:30:31,739
 There's also a hat. 

359
00:30:31,739 --> 00:30:35,004
 I don't need it anymore. Keeping this takes up space. 
 I don't need it anymore. 

360
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:52,459
 You may like this cat because it plays with you,
  meows and catches mice, 

361
00:30:52,459 --> 00:30:55,260
 but not because it looks like Chun Lu. 

362
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:57,919
 Is Chun Lu easily replaceable? 

363
00:30:57,919 --> 00:31:00,480
 I didn't replace Chun Lu with the kitten. 

364
00:31:01,539 --> 00:31:06,459
 It just keeps me company. 
 It helps ease my mind when I'm upset. 

365
00:31:19,119 --> 00:31:22,980
 Why should I care if he is upset? 

366
00:31:28,639 --> 00:31:31,999
