393
00:32:48,280 --> 00:32:49,880
Webmaster!

394
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:53,200
Guan Lan! Guan Lan, why are you silent?

395
00:32:57,536 --> 00:32:59,584
Come on.

396
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:05,679
What did you write? Show me.

397
00:33:16,679 --> 00:33:19,259
Class Monitor, why don't you help—

398
