Jiang Qiao Xi is attending 
 a Math Olympiad lecture.

399
00:33:22,999 --> 00:33:26,379
Can someone collect his assignments 
 for all his classes?

400
00:33:26,379 --> 00:33:28,340
Teacher, I'll do it.

401
00:33:35,620 --> 00:33:37,396
What's wrong?

402
00:33:38,500 --> 00:33:40,568
Nothing.

403
00:33:59,959 --> 00:34:01,784
Meow!

404
00:34:03,319 --> 00:34:07,100
There you are. Are you waiting for me?

405
00:34:08,619 --> 00:34:11,400
I brought you something tasty.

406
00:34:17,199 --> 00:34:19,299
Good kitty!

407
00:34:20,579 --> 00:34:23,139
Did you have a good day?

408
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:29,019
Are you happy when you're alone?

409
00:34:33,240 --> 00:34:37,720
Take good care of yourself when alone.

410
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:44,040
Make sure to eat well and keep warm.

411
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:47,959
 You are very important to me, 

412
00:34:47,959 --> 00:34:55,239
 so you must be healthy and happy. 
 All right? 

413
00:34:56,559 --> 00:35:02,179
You must be happy, healthy, and safe. 
 All right?

414
00:35:02,179 --> 00:35:09,480
You are very important to me.

415
00:35:16,159 --> 00:35:18,036
Hurry up!

416
