Isn't that right? Just look how soaked I am!

418
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:27,540
I'm completely soaked!

419
00:35:29,979 --> 00:35:33,320
It's so annoying. It may rain all night.

420
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:35,400
The rain is great. We can sleep better.

421
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:37,099
Isn't that right, Cherry?

422
00:35:37,099 --> 00:35:38,999
You two may get some sleep.

423
00:35:38,999 --> 00:35:41,839
I can't fall asleep when it rains.

424
00:35:42,420 --> 00:35:45,519
You're so carefree. How can a little rain 
 stop you from sleeping?

425
00:35:45,519 --> 00:35:47,680
It's not the sound of rain 
 that keeps me awake.

426
00:35:47,680 --> 00:35:50,400
On rainy days, the neighborhood cats 
 keep meowing.

427
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:52,180
They make noise until late at night. 
 How can I sleep?

428
00:35:52,180 --> 00:35:54,464
Are there really cats? 
 Why haven't I heard them?

429
00:35:54,464 --> 00:35:55,619
- Let's get on! 
 - Let's get on!

430
00:35:55,619 --> 00:35:56,660
Stop scaring me. Hurry up!

