00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:38,439
Let's go.

448
00:38:38,439 --> 00:38:39,860
Let's go. Good kitty.

449
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:42,479
I'm here to help you.

450
00:38:42,479 --> 00:38:45,800
Go up there. Go ahead.

451
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:47,872
Let's go.

452
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:09,720
Lin Cherry, what are you doing here?

453
00:39:09,720 --> 00:39:11,264
What are you doing here?

454
00:39:11,264 --> 00:39:13,920
Shouldn't I be the one asking you?

455
00:39:15,160 --> 00:39:18,159
Enough! Help me up first.

456
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:20,504
Hurry up!

457
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:28,620
Didn't you say 
 we are just regular classmates?

458
00:39:29,240 --> 00:39:34,300
Who would risk everything to this extent, 
 for a classmate's cat?

459
00:39:35,620 --> 00:39:38,059
Is now the right time for this conversation?

460
00:39:38,059 --> 00:39:40,519
Can't you help me up first?

461
00:39:40,519 --> 00:39:43,019
I should be the one to rescue my own cat.

462
00:39:43,579 --> 00:39:45,619
Why did you step in?

463
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:53,459
Are you the only one 
 who can be compassionate?

464
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:56,820
Stop lying to yourself.

465
00:39:56,820 --> 00:39:59,099
We can't be just regular classmates.

466
00:39:59,099 --> 00:40:02,340
Everything you've done for me 
 has long surpassed that level.

467
00:40:02,340 --> 00:40:04,040
Do you admit it?

468
00:40:04,740 --> 00:40:06,580
That's not true.

469
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:13,740
The more you deny it, 
 the more you prove it's true!

470
00:40:15,260 --> 00:40:17,200
You're shallow.

471
00:40:17,200 --> 00:40:19,200
I'm shallow?

472
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:22,759
Fine, I'm shallow. I'm leaving.

473
00:40:22,759 --> 00:40:25,619
Don't go! Jiang Qiao Xi, don't go!

474
00:40:25,619 --> 00:40:27,059
Come back!

475
00:40:27,059 --> 00:40:30,400
Fine. You're Jiang Qiao Xi,

476
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:33,890
the top student in our class, 
 and Jialin's Math Olympiad genius!

477
00:40:33,899 --> 00:40:38,179
You're… You're handsome 
 and you have a great voice.

478
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:43,800
Is that it? I'm also tall.

479
00:40:44,499 --> 00:40:48,439
Yes, you're tall. Isn't that enough?

480
00:40:48,439 --> 00:40:50,419
That's why I treat you in a special way.

481
00:40:50,419 --> 00:40:52,200
