482
00:40:52,200 --> 00:40:54,180
What's so strange about that? 
 What's there to be proud of?

483
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:57,839
You treat me in a special way. 
 Of course, this makes me feel proud.

484
00:40:59,700 --> 00:41:03,499
Now that you're done being proud, 
 can you help me get up?

485
00:41:04,119 --> 00:41:07,580
Come on, give me your hand.

486
00:41:10,459 --> 00:41:12,360
I can't get up like this.

487
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:15,539
Come down. I'll step on you to get up.

488
00:41:15,539 --> 00:41:17,368
- Should I get down there? 
 - Yes.

489
00:41:18,119 --> 00:41:19,700
Fine.

490
00:41:20,499 --> 00:41:23,139
It's so high. How did you get down there?

491
00:41:31,539 --> 00:41:33,160
Let's go.

492
00:41:33,980 --> 00:41:36,320
- Come on. 
 - Squat down.

493
00:41:37,900 --> 00:41:39,419
Be careful! Come on.

494
00:41:39,419 --> 00:41:41,039
How do I get up?

495
00:41:41,039 --> 00:41:43,639
- I'll give you a lift. 
 - I'll step on your leg.

496
00:41:48,680 --> 00:41:50,552
Careful with your leg.

497
00:41:59,280 --> 00:42:01,099
Come on! Pull me up.

498
00:42:01,099 --> 00:42:04,039
Aren't you tall? Get up here yourself.

499
00:42:04,039 --> 00:42:05,340
And you were right.

500
00:42:05,340 --> 00:42:07,500
You should take care of your own cat.

501
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:09,059
I shouldn't have stepped in.

502
00:42:09,059 --> 00:42:11,359
I didn't lie to myself.

503
00:42:11,359 --> 00:42:13,108
Lin Cherry!

504
00:42:31,680 --> 00:42:36,919
Kitty, come here. Are you okay?

505
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:43,419
Be good. Don't run around.

